        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>G.I. and Veterans Education Empowerment Act or the GIVE Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Veterans Affairs to provide veterans and members of the Armed Forces with information about whether (1) a postsecondary education institution is listed on the College Navigator website as being affiliated with a certain religion, (2) an institution is minority serving, and (3) an institution is gender specific.<br> </p>]]>
        </text>
